title: Stop cards from flashing when returning from info activity
message:
Stop cards from flashing when returning from info activity

The changes made here actually mean that changing the rating while in the info activity won't cause it to be updated when returning to the list.

If we also update the tags though, it will be, since for some reason those updates always go through.

Hopefully a nice way of fixing this will be presented in the future, but I'm not so worried about it for now.

title: Finally got the tag drawing exactly how I want it
message:
Finally got the tag drawing exactly how I want it

We now only round the corners on the start of a tag and on the end of a tag if it starts and ends on that line. We use a rounded rectangle path instead of a rounded rectangle to do so, Canvas.drawRoundRect() doesn't support defining specific corners' radii, and Path.addRoundRect() does. We also don't bother trying to draw on lines which are past our max.
